 ‚àá start
 ‚çù Starts the web server for the UW Schedule Exporter application
 ‚çù
 ‚çù This function initializes and starts a Jarvis web server on port 8080
 ‚çù with the following configuration:
 ‚çù - Port: 8080
 ‚çù - Namespace: web (contains request handlers)
 ‚çù - Payload format: JSON
 ‚çù - Default page: Index function in web namespace
 ‚çù - Allows both GET and POST requests
 ‚çù
 ‚çù Global variables created:
 ‚çù - JSrv: Jarvis server instance for later control (stop, restart, etc.)
 ‚çù
 ‚çù Usage: start
 ‚çù After running, the web interface will be available at http://localhost:8080
      JSrv‚ÜêJarvis.New(8111 web'JSON')
      JSrv.DYALOG_JARVIS_THREAD‚Üê'0'
      JSrv.Debug‚Üê0
      JSrv.HTMLInterface‚Üê'' 'Index'
      JSrv.AllowGETs‚Üê1
      JSrv.AllowPOSTs‚Üê1
      JSrv.Start
 ‚àá
